cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with pre-training methods for medical image classifiers, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method involves unsupervised task design, which is related to unsupervised learning (cs.AI) and meta-learning (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper uses a breast DCE-MRI dataset, which is a medical imaging modality, and therefore, the paper could also be categorized under neural engineering (cs.NE).
